sub_title: Senior Manager Data Standardisation & Technical Asset Operations – Subsurface Data universe SDU/(o)SDU Transformation team at Shell
summary: Experienced energy industry professional with 16 years of progressive leadership in oil and gas IT. Proven track record in driving business strategy, digital transformation, and M&A initiatives. Currently spearheading global cloud standardization at Shell, leading a diverse team across regions. A strategic leader adept at aligning technology with business objectives, delivering high-value projects, and enabling cross-organizational collaboration. Dedicated to proactively driving our software portfolio towards a net-zero carbon footprint, while harnessing the power of cloud technologies. Committed to leading the organization through the transformational journey, capitalizing on sustainable practices and innovative cloud solutions to achieve both environmental stewardship and competitive advantage.
